{{! ----- i18n ----- }}
<section id="feature-i18n">
<h3>Languages</h3>

<p>The plugin ships with full translations for: Afrikaans, German, Greek,
Spanish, French, Hebrew, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Swahili, Xhosa,
Zulu — alongside English. Set the language via Moodle's standard user /
site language preferences.</p>

<p>Strings used by client-side code are loaded via the standard
<code>core/str</code> module rather than hard-coded; a missing translation
falls back to English without breaking the UI.</p>
</section>
